/-! ## Project-local Mathlib supplement вҖ” `jShriekOU` transport along a scheme iso (Need #1)

The corepresenting object `jShriekOU V` of `О“(V,-)` is carried along a scheme isomorphism
`ПҶ : X вү… Y` by the induced pushforward equivalence: `ОҰ.functor (jShriekOU V) вү… jShriekOU (ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V)`.
The argument is pure corepresentability transport вҖ” `jShriekOU V` is never unfolded.  Both sides
corepresent the *same* `Type`-valued sections functor `О“(ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V,-)`: the right side directly (the
additive corepresentability `jShriekOU_homEquiv`), the left side via the pushforward adjunction
(`ОҰ.functor вҠЈ ОҰ.inverse`) composed with the definitional identity "sections of a pushforward =
sections over the preimage open".  `CorepresentableBy.uniqueUpToIso` then produces the iso. -/

/-- **`jShriekOU V` corepresents the `Type`-valued sections functor `О“(V,-)`.**  Repackages the
additive corepresentability `jShriekOU_homEquiv` as a `CorepresentableBy` of `sectionsFunctor V`
post-composed with the forgetful functor to types. Project-local. -/
private noncomputable def sectionsCorep {X : Scheme.{u}} (V : TopologicalSpace.Opens X) :
    (sectionsFunctor V вӢҷ forget AddCommGrpCat).CorepresentableBy (jShriekOU V) where
  homEquiv {B} := (jShriekOU_homEquiv V B).toEquiv
  homEquiv_comp g f := jShriekOU_homEquiv_nat V f g

/-- **The pushforward of `jShriekOU V` corepresents `О“(ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V,-)`.**  Via the pushforward
adjunction `ОҰ.functor вҠЈ ОҰ.inverse` and the definitional identity "sections of `ПҶ.inv`-pushforward
over `V` = sections over `ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V`", the object `ОҰ.functor (jShriekOU V)` corepresents the same
`Type`-valued sections functor as `jShriekOU (ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V)`.  Project-local. -/
private noncomputable def sectionsCorepPushforward {X Y : Scheme.{u}} (ПҶ : X вү… Y)
    (V : TopologicalSpace.Opens X) :
    (sectionsFunctor (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ V) вӢҷ forget AddCommGrpCat).CorepresentableBy
      ((Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).functor.obj (jShriekOU V)) where
  homEquiv {B} :=
    ((Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).toAdjunction.homEquiv (jShriekOU V) B).trans
      (jShriekOU_homEquiv V ((Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).inverse.obj B)).toEquiv
  homEquiv_comp {B B'} g f := by
    simp only [Equiv.trans_apply]
    rw [(Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).toAdjunction.homEquiv_naturality_right]
    erw [jShriekOU_homEquiv_nat V
      ((Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).toAdjunction.homEquiv (jShriekOU V) B f)
      ((Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).inverse.map g)]

/-- **A scheme isomorphism carries `jShriekOU` along** (blueprint `lem:jshriek_transport_along_iso`).
For `ПҶ : X вү… Y` and an open `V вҠҶ X`, the pushforward equivalence sends the corepresenting object of
`О“(V,-)` to that of `О“(ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V,-)`:
`ОҰ.functor (jShriekOU V) вү… jShriekOU (ПҶ.invвҒ»В№V)`.  Project-local: the geometric naturality of `j_!`
under a scheme iso (the first-`Ext`-argument transport of Need #1). -/
noncomputable def jShriekOU_transport_along_iso {X Y : Scheme.{u}} (ПҶ : X вү… Y)
    (V : TopologicalSpace.Opens X) :
    (Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).functor.obj (jShriekOU V) вү…
      jShriekOU (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ V) :=
  (sectionsCorepPushforward ПҶ V).uniqueUpToIso (sectionsCorep (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ V))

/-! ## Project-local Mathlib supplement вҖ” quasi-coherence transport along a scheme iso (`hqc`) -/

/-- **A scheme isomorphism transports an open cover.** If a family `Z` of opens covers `X`
(in the sense of the opens Grothendieck topology, i.e. `CoversTop`), then the preimage family
`ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ (Z i)` covers `Y`.  Project-local: the cover-transport half of
`pushforward_iso_preserves_qcoh` (Need #1 `hqc`). -/
private lemma coversTop_preimage_of_iso {X Y : Scheme.{u}} (ПҶ : X вү… Y) {I : Type*}
    (Z : I вҶ’ X.Opens) (hZ : (Opens.grothendieckTopology X).CoversTop Z) :
    (Opens.grothendieckTopology Y).CoversTop (fun i => ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Z i) := by
  intro W x hx
  obtain вҹЁU', f, hf, hU'вҹ© := hZ вҠӨ (ПҶ.inv.base x) (by trivial)
  obtain вҹЁi, вҹЁgвҹ©вҹ© := hf
  have hxZ : ПҶ.inv.base x вҲҲ Z i := (leOfHom g) hU'
  refine вҹЁW вҠ“ (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Z i), homOfLE inf_le_left,
    вҹЁi, вҹЁhomOfLE inf_le_rightвҹ©вҹ©, вҹЁhx, ?_вҹ©вҹ©
  exact hxZ

