/-- **The slice structure-sheaf ring map `ПҲ_r`** (blueprint `lem:slice_structureSheaf_hom`).  The
over-pullback (to the slice `Over Uбөў`) of the structure-sheaf comparison `ПҶ.inv.toRingCatSheafHom`.
Its codomain is the sliced pushforward of `рқ’Ә_Y` along `Over.post (Opens.map ПҶ.inv.base)`, identified
with the over-pullback of the un-sliced pushforward by the BeckвҖ“Chevalley `rfl`-equality
`Over.post F вӢҷ Over.forget = Over.forget вӢҷ F`.  Project-local: the single cross-ring datum from
which `SheafOfModules.pullback ПҲ_r` (Need #1 `hqc`) is built. -/
noncomputable def sliceStructureSheafHom : (X.ringCatSheaf.over Ui) вҹ¶
    ((Over.post (X := Ui) (Opens.map ПҶ.inv.base)).sheafPushforwardContinuous RingCat
      ((Opens.grothendieckTopology X).over Ui)
      ((Opens.grothendieckTopology Y).over (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui))).obj
        (Y.ringCatSheaf.over (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui)) :=
