/-! ## Project-local Mathlib supplement вҖ” slice equivalence for `ПҶ : X вү… Y` and its continuity

The slice equivalence `Over Uбөў вүҢ Over Vбөў` (`Vбөў = ПҶ.invвҒ»В№бөҒ Uбөў`) induced by a scheme iso `ПҶ`, with
