  вҖў HвӮҒ = `pushforwardSliceAdjunctionH1`, HвӮӮ = `pushforwardSliceAdjunctionH2`: the counit/unit
    compatibility squares.  Both reference `ПҶ''.hom`, so they are unprovable until ПҶ'' is concrete; once
    ПҶ'' lands they reduce to proof-irrelevant `eqToHom = eqToHom` squares (blueprint).
  вҖў `pushforwardSlicePullbackIso` section identity (the `вүӘвү« sorry`): the rfl-clean
    `(pushforward ПҶ'').obj (H.over Uбөў) вү… (ОҰ H).over Vбөў` (`Scheme.Modules.pushforward_obj_obj`); also
    blocked on concrete ПҶ''.
-/

/-- **Counit compatibility square `HвӮҒ`** for the slice adjunction (blueprint
`lem:pushforward_slice_adjunction_h1`).  The reverse ring map `ПҶ''` and the forward slice ring map
`ПҲ_r` satisfy the counit-naturality square required by `pushforwardPushforwardAdj`, absorbing the
`Over.map (unitIso.inv)` correction of the inverse functor (reduces to a proof-irrelevant
equality-transport identity along `ПҶ.homвҒ»В№бөҒ (ПҶ.invвҒ»В№бөҒ Uбөў) = Uбөў`). -/
lemma pushforwardSliceAdjunctionH1 :
    Functor.whiskerRight (NatTrans.op (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.toAdjunction.counit)
        (Sheaf.over X.ringCatSheaf Ui).obj =
      (sliceStructureSheafHom ПҶ Ui).hom вү«
        (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.inverse.op.whiskerLeft (sliceReverseRingMap ПҶ Ui).hom := by
  sorry

/-- **Unit compatibility square `HвӮӮ`** for the slice adjunction (blueprint
`lem:pushforward_slice_adjunction_h2`).  Identical in shape to `HвӮҒ`: the unit triangle reduces to a
proof-irrelevant equality-transport identity along the same open identity. -/
lemma pushforwardSliceAdjunctionH2 :
    (sliceReverseRingMap ПҶ Ui).hom вү«
        (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.functor.op.whiskerLeft (sliceStructureSheafHom ПҶ Ui).hom вү«
          Functor.whiskerRight (NatTrans.op (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.toAdjunction.unit)
            (Sheaf.over Y.ringCatSheaf (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui)).obj =
      рқҹҷ (Sheaf.over Y.ringCatSheaf (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui)).obj := by
  sorry

/-- **The two-pushforward slice adjunction** (blueprint `lem:pushforward_slice_two_adjunction`):
`pushforward ПҶ'' вҠЈ pushforward ПҲ_r`, assembled by feeding `pushforwardPushforwardAdj` the slice
equivalence's adjunction, the two ring maps `ПҶ''`/`ПҲ_r`, and the compatibility squares `HвӮҒ`/`HвӮӮ`. -/
noncomputable def pushforwardSliceTwoAdjunction :
    SheafOfModules.pushforward.{u} (sliceReverseRingMap ПҶ Ui) вҠЈ
      SheafOfModules.pushforward.{u} (sliceStructureSheafHom ПҶ Ui) := by
  haveI hF : (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.functor.IsContinuous
      ((Opens.grothendieckTopology Y).over (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui))
      ((Opens.grothendieckTopology X).over Ui) :=
    sliceOversEquiv_inverse_isContinuous ПҶ Ui
  haveI hG : (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.inverse.IsContinuous
      ((Opens.grothendieckTopology X).over Ui)
      ((Opens.grothendieckTopology Y).over (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui)) :=
    sliceOversEquiv_functor_isContinuous ПҶ Ui
  exact SheafOfModules.pushforwardPushforwardAdj
    (sliceOversEquiv ПҶ Ui).symm.toAdjunction
    (sliceReverseRingMap ПҶ Ui) (sliceStructureSheafHom ПҶ Ui)
    (pushforwardSliceAdjunctionH1 ПҶ Ui) (pushforwardSliceAdjunctionH2 ПҶ Ui)

/-- **The slice pullback comparison iso** (blueprint `lem:pushforward_slice_pullback_iso`).  Applying
the pullback `pullback ПҲ_r` to the slice `H.over Uбөў` is isomorphic to the restricted pushforward
`(ОҰ H).over Vбөў`.  Step 1: `pullback ПҲ_r вү… pushforward ПҶ''` by uniqueness of left adjoints
(`leftAdjointUniq` of `pullbackPushforwardAdjunction ПҲ_r` against `pushforwardSliceTwoAdjunction`).
Step 2: the rfl-clean section identity `(pushforward ПҶ'').obj (H.over Uбөў) вү… (ОҰ H).over Vбөў`
(both sides have sections `О“(H, ПҶ.homвҒ»В№бөҒ W.left)` by `pushforward_obj_obj`). -/
noncomputable def pushforwardSlicePullbackIso (H : X.Modules) :
    (SheafOfModules.pullback.{u} (sliceStructureSheafHom ПҶ Ui)).obj (H.over Ui) вү…
      ((Scheme.Modules.pushforwardEquivOfIso ПҶ).functor.obj H).over (ПҶ.inv вҒ»В№бөҒ Ui) :=
  (Adjunction.leftAdjointUniq
    (SheafOfModules.pullbackPushforwardAdjunction.{u} (sliceStructureSheafHom ПҶ Ui))
    (pushforwardSliceTwoAdjunction ПҶ Ui)).app (H.over Ui) вүӘвү« sorry

